### Favorites Management Endpoints

### Get Favorite Foods
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/favorites/foods
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Favorite Restaurants
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/favorites/restaurants
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Add Favorite Food
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/favorites/foods/food-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Remove Favorite Food
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/favorites/foods/food-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Add Favorite Restaurant
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/favorites/restaurants/restaurant-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Remove Favorite Restaurant
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/favorites/restaurants/restaurant-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Check Food Favorite Status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/favorites/foods/food-123/status
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Check Restaurant Favorite Status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/favorites/restaurants/restaurant-123/status
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Toggle Food Favorite
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/favorites/foods/food-123/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Toggle Restaurant Favorite
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/favorites/restaurants/restaurant-123/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Clear All Favorites
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/favorites
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Favorites Stats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/favorites/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Favorite Foods Stream (Not Implemented - WebSocket)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/favorites/foods/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

